    "plan_content": "Here's the complete implementation plan for the PulseBoard channel plugin.\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\nThe plan creates **~25 production files + 8 test files** entirely under `extensions/pulseboard/`, mirroring the IRC plugin structure (the best analog — it supports both DM and group, uses WebSocket-style connection monitor, and `createChatChannelPlugin`).\n\n### Files to create\n\n**Root wiring (7):** `package.json`, `openclaw.plugin.json`, `index.ts`, `setup-entry.ts`, `api.ts`, `channel-config-api.ts`, `runtime-api.ts`\n\n**`src/` files (17):**\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `channel.ts` | `createChatChannelPlugin` — `chatTypes: [\"direct\",\"group\"]`, `textChunkLimit: 4000` |\n| `client.ts` | Fictional WebSocket API client (auth handshake, send, disconnect) |\n| `monitor.ts` | Connection loop → `handlePulseBoardInbound` on each incoming event |\n| `inbound.ts` | Full DM+group dispatch: policy gates → pairing → mention → `dispatchInboundReplyWithBase` |\n| `send.ts` | Outbound send (live client or transient WebSocket) |\n| `accounts.ts` | Multi-account resolution with `PULSEBOARD_SERVER_URL/API_KEY/USERNAME` env vars |\n| `config-schema.ts` | Zod schemas with `DmPolicySchema`, `GroupPolicySchema`, per-board groups |\n| `normalize.ts` | `pulseboard:`, `board:`, `user:` prefix stripping; `#`-prefix for board targets |\n| `policy.ts` | Board group access gates, require-mention, sender allowlist |\n| `probe.ts` | Health check via short-lived WebSocket connect |\n| `setup-core.ts` / `setup-surface.ts` | Config patchers + interactive wizard |\n| `types.ts`, `protocol.ts`, `config-ui-hints.ts`, `runtime.ts`, `runtime-api.ts` | Supporting infrastructure |\n\n**Key design decisions:**\n- `textChunkLimit: 4000` as specified\n- `runtime-api.ts` re-exports from `openclaw/plugin-sdk/irc` (a registered public subpath that exposes generic `dispatchInboundReplyWithBase` and channel dispatch utilities — no `src/plugin-sdk/pulseboard.ts` can be created under this task's \"only create files in pulseboard extension directory\" constraint)\n- Config path: `channels.pulseboard`, board groups under `channels.pulseboard.groups`\n- No external npm dependencies (pure WebSocket)",
